<h2>Castle Rock Reading Order</h2>

Check this <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Castle_Rock_(Stephen_King)">Wikipedia link about Castle Rock</a>.<br><br>

The following are the important Castle Rock stories.

<ul>
<li>The Dead Zone (1979)</li>
<li>Cujo (1981)</li>
<li>The Body (1982)</li>
<li>Uncle Otto's Truck (1983, collected in Skeleton Crew, 1985)</li>
<li>Gramma (1984, collected in Skeleton Crew, 1985)</li>
<li>Mrs. Todd's Shortcut (1984, collected in Skeleton Crew, 1985)</li>
<li>Nona (first published as a Castle Rock story in 1985)</li>
<li>The Dark Half (1989)</li>
<li>The Sun Dog (1990)</li>
<li>Needful Things (1991)</li>
<li>It Grows on You (first published as a Castle Rock story in 1993)</li>
<li>The Man in the Black Suit (1994, collected in Everything's Eventual, 2002)</li>
<li>Bag of Bones (1998)</li>
<li>Premium Harmony (2009)</li>
</ul>

